data.value:
Dark souls Death Counter by Fortunecookie103.
A simple program made for streamers who want to keep count of their deaths in Dark Souls or other games. Can very easily be integrated in Xsplit or OBS. Simply open your streaming program of choice, and create a new textbox. Select "Text from textfile". Select the file "deaths.txt" created by 'Death Counter'. The file can be found in the directory: C:\Users/User/Documents/Deathcounter/Deaths.txt
